3. ❌ **Code examples**: git commands, test code → Reference workflows/guides
4. ❌ **Missing "Rule:" title** → Must start with "Rule:"
5. ❌ **No quality gates** → Each phase must have quality gate
6. ❌ **Detailed implementation**: Backend/frontend code patterns → Reference guides
7. ❌ **Too long** (300-400 lines) → Target 75-85 lines
